# Pantheon-Prime Roadmap v1.0

Pantheon-Prime is a cognitive operating system kernel designed for long-horizon
LLM reasoning, deterministic safety, and multi-model governance.

This roadmap defines the flagship demonstrations and milestones.

## 1. Flagship Demos
- Infinity Memory Chat (100-Day Demo)
- Multi-Model Triangulation Engine
- Safe Autonomous Research Agent
- Pantheon Notebook (Governed Cells)

## 2. Kernel Milestones
- v1.1 Merkle Warden Hardening
- v1.2 Daemon Contract Schema
- v2.0 Multi-Agent Orchestration

## 3. Experimental Tracks
- Continuity Stress Tests
- Invariant Robustness Testing
- Cross-Model Narrative Stability

## 4. Theory Extensions
