ğŸ“˜ 7. API Spec

Save as: api/pantheon_api_spec.md

# PantheonOS API Specification

## Core Endpoints

### /compute
Runs an LLM inference step under deterministic governance.

### /state/get
Returns StateVector snapshot.

### /state/commit
Commits a ThoughtObject.

### /daemon/run/<name>
Executes a daemon operation with full audit logging.


